'From Squeak2.6 of 11 October 1999 [latest update: #1708] on 10 December 1999 at 12:49:30 pm'!"Change Set:		alphabetize-thDate:			8 December 1999Author:			Torge HusfeldtImplements the alphabetize feature for method-category lists.Tweaked by sw such that it asks before discarding unsubmitted code."!!Browser methodsFor: 'message category functions' stamp: 'th 12/08/99 (+sw tweak)'!alphabetizeMessageCategories	classListIndex = 0		ifTrue: [^ false].	self okToChange ifFalse: [^ false].	self classOrMetaClassOrganizer categories: self rawMessageCategoryList asSortedCollection asArray.	Smalltalk changes reorganizeClass: self selectedClassOrMetaClass.	self clearUserEditFlag.	self editClass.	self classListIndex: classListIndex.	^ true! !